从氟化银到碘化银，卤化银的溶解度逐渐降低，氯化银、溴化银和碘化银都是难溶于水的。它们的溶解度数据列在下表中：<ref name="CRC">Lide, David R. (ed). (2005) ''Handbook of Chemistry and Physics'', 86th Edition, The Chemical Rubber Publishing Co., Cleveland. </ref>

{| class="wikitable" style="margin: 1em auto"
